                  </tr>                       <tr>    <th class="x-th-fund">存续期限</th>          <td class="x-td-fund">无固定限期</td>                  <th class="x-th-fund">封闭期</th>          <td class="x-td-fund">本基金成立起6个月之内不可赎回</td>        </tr>        <tr>          <th class="x-th-fund">开放日</th>          <td class="x-td-fund">每月最后一个交易日开放一次，接受投资者认购</td>        </tr>      </tbody></table><h2 class="x-tt-blue"><span style="margin-left:20px">认购详情</span></h2><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="mb10 x-tb-fund                                                                                                        "><tbody><tr>          <th class="x-th-fund">认购门槛</th>          <td class="x-td-fund">封闭运行中，不再接受认购</td>                  <th class="x-th-fund">认购费用</th>          <td class="x-td-fund">无</td>        </tr><tr>          <th class="x-th-fund">赎回费用</th>          <td class="x-td-fund">成立之日起6个月内不允许赎回；投资者持有本基金时间多于6个月但少于12个月发生赎回时，将被收取2%的赎回费用</td>        <th class="x-th-fund">管理费</th> <td class="x-td-fund">1.5%</td>         </tr><tr>          <th class="x-th-fund">券商财务顾问费（外包服务费）</th>          <td class="x-td-fund">0.25%，每日计提，按月支付。（托管费0.1%+运营费0.15%）</td>                  <th class="x-th-fund">管理费计提及结算方式</th>          <td class="x-td-fund">基金管理人管理费、券商管理费与托管费每日计提，按月支付</td>        </tr><tr>          <th class="x-th-fund">投资者分红方式</th>          <td class="x-td-fund">基金累计单位净值大于1.1时，在当月最后一个工作日以当日基金单位净值大于1.1的部分作为现金分红</td>                  <th class="x-th-fund">基金管理人业绩计提标准</th>          <td class="x-td-fund">本基金在份额净值创新高时（以扣除相关产品计提费用后的净值为参照）按30%计提业绩报酬</td>        </tr></tbody></table><h2 class="x-tt-blue"><span style="margin-left:20px">投资详情</span></h2><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="mb10 x-tb-fund                                                                                                        "><tbody><tr>          <th class="x-th-fund">投资标的</th>          <td class="x-td-fund">上海证券交易所、深圳证券交易所公开挂牌交易的股票（包括新股申购）</td>                  <th class="x-th-fund">团队简介</th>          <td class="x-td-fund"><strong>操作手法特点：</strong>先利用1-2个月的时间选定1-2支可行股票，为建仓作布局，待时机一到，100%仓位购入，紧密监看盈亏情况，快进快出，来回操作，以最短时间实现利润最大化。<br /><strong>适合客户群：</strong>激进型投资者，喜欢赚快钱，同时也能承受较高风险。<br /><strong>操盘理念：</strong>牛市，就该用【快牛】政策；牛市降临空观望，辗转十载方恨迟！</td>        </tr></tbody></table>";}i:7;a:3:{s:2:"id";s:4:"2395";s:5:"field";s:8:"content1";s:3:"val";s:19206:"<svg version="1.1" style="font-family:SimSun," font-size:12px="" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="715" height="310"><desc>Created with Highstock 2.0.1</desc><defs><clippath id="highcharts-1"><rect x="0" y="0" width="646" height="182"></rect></clippath><clippath id="highcharts-2"><rect x="0" y="0" width="646" height="183"></rect></clippath><clippath id="highcharts-4"><rect x="0" y="0" width="646" height="28"></rect></clippath></defs><rect x="0" y="0" width="715" height="310" strokewidth="0" fill="#FFFFFF" class=" highcharts-background"></rect><rect x="49" y="60" width="646" height="183" fill="none" isshadow="true" stroke="#000000" stroke-opacity="0.049999999999999996" stroke-width="5" transform="translate(1, 1)"></rect><rect x="49" y="60" width="646" height="183" fill="none" isshadow="true" stroke="#000000" stroke-opacity="0.09999999999999999" stroke-width="3" transform="translate(1, 1)"></rect><rect x="49" y="60" width="646" height="183" fill="none" isshadow="true" stroke="#000000" stroke-opacity="0.15" stroke-width="1" transform="translate(1, 1)"></rect><rect x="49" y="60" width="646" height="183" fill="#ffffff"></rect><text x="49" y="40" style="color:black;fill:black;"></text><path fill="rgba(170,70,67,0.25)" d="M 0 0"></path><path fill="rgba(69,114,167,0.25)" d="M 0 0"></path><g class="highcharts-grid" zindex="1"><path fill="none" d="M 283.5 60 L 283.5 243" stroke="#C0C0C0" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4,3" zindex="1" opacity="1"></path><path fill="none" d="M 351.5 60 L 351.5 243" stroke="#C0C0C0" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4,3" zindex="1" opaci